        "new_rules_in_this_unit": [
            "Form genitive case for possession: des + r-word/s-word noun + -s/-es, der + e-word noun, der + plural noun; the genitive modifier follows the main noun.",
            "Add -s to proper names for genitive (no apostrophe), unless the name ends in -s/-ß/-x/-z.",
            "Apply n-declension for r-words like der Mensch: add -n/-en in accusative, dative, and genitive (des Menschen) instead of -s/-es."
        ],
